data.description: This is a short sale and has to be approved with Veterans United. Wait... Do you hear that.... No just peace and quite here.  Nestled on 2.38 MOL acres just about 1/2 block from Hwy 412 in Ringwood sits the beautiful home.  4 or 5 bedroom with a possible Large recreation room upstairs.  This floor plan will please almost everyone.  Granite through-out.  A built in coffee bar.  a double sided fireplace from the dining room to the living room. Dual CHA.   Sit outside on the front porch or the side fire pit area, enjoy that coffee and watch for wild life to walk through your property.  Perched up on a hill for that great view.  Has a 5 barbed wired fence around the property, has a newer (2023) septic and lateral lines.  Pictures just don't capture the beauty of this mini ranch.  Make an appointment today.
